  m_text: "Controls:\n\nWASD - WALKING\n\nLSHIFT - DASH kill\n\nLMB - Shoot\n\nEnemies:\n\nThe
    weak\t\t: Mediocre Enemy\tPenetration: 1\nNote\t\t: honestly, score farming.\n\nThe
    Chainer\t: Fast Enemy\tPenetration: 0\nNote\t\t: This foe could limit your bullet
    penetration.\n\nThe Sawfish\t: Invincible enemy\tPenetration: 0\nNOte\t\t: Utilize
    your dashing, partner.\n\nThe Bomber\t: AOE Enemy\tPenetration: 1\nNote\t\t:
    The only foe could damage you, avoid at all cost!"
